::Rex::

Rex opens his mouth to answer Gangon, being interrupted by a loud clang. He 
frowns.

"I'll be right back," he says, walking toward the source of the sound and 
nearly crashing into Feline as he exits the room and rounds the corner. He 
jumps back, gun ready.

"What's going on?" he asks, keeping his gun ready just in case as he looks at 
the computer and bot parts on the floor and in Feline's arms.
